Fayulu amisakoli president mpe asengi na ba Congolais kondima Tshisekedi te






"Bato nyonso bakomona bopesani ya bokonzi ya bato bakola (civilisé) mpe na kimya nyonso," ebakisi moko ya présidence.
Pene na bakonzi zomi ya mboka ya Afrika bakozala wana, kolanda na maloba baye basololi na VOA Lingala.